nia      博士<br>1998     吉林大学              学士<br>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon2\">工作经历</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     2013-\t北京大学数学科学学院\t教授<br>2007-2013\t北京大学数学科学学院\t副教授<br>2010-2010\t美国特拉华大学数学科学系\t客座副教授<br>2006-2007\t北京大学数学科学学院\t助理教授<br>2005-2006\t东京工业大学数学科学系\t客座副教授<br>2004-2005\t波士顿学院数学系\t讲师\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                   <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon3\">代表作</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                    C. Song and B. Yao, On combinatorial rectangles with minimum infinity-discrepancy, Enumer. Comb. Appl. 1 (2021), no.1, Paper No. S2R7. <br><br>C. Magnant, C. Song and S. Xia, Colored graph homomorphisms, Rocky Mountain J. Math. 49 (2019), no.8, 2717-2737. <br><br>H. Hu, T. Mansour and C. Song, On the maximal independence polynomial of certain graph configurations, Rocky Mountain J. Math. 47 (2017), no.7, 2219-2253. <br><br>Z. Dong, W. V. Li and C. Song, Integral representations for binomial sums of chances of winning, Ars Math. Contemp. 12 (2017), no.2, 329-336. <br><br>C. Song and C.H. Yan, Descents of permutations in a Ferrers board, The Electronic Journal of Combinatorics 19 (2012), R7. \n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon5\">主讲课程</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                    2008.9-\t高等代数I\t数学学院/元培08级本科生<br><br>2008.2-2008.6\t高等代数II\t数学学院/元培07级本科生<br><br>2007.9-2008.1\t高等代数I\t数学学院/元培07级本科生<br><br>2007.2-2007.6\t组合数学\t数学学院本科生、研究生<br><br>2006.9-2007.1\t文科高等数学\t中文/哲学/社会学06级本科生\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"subInfo01\">\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_title subInfo01_title1\"><h3 class=\"t_icon7\">社会兼职</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"subInfo01_Con1\">\n                     十三届、十二届中国数学会理事<br>十三届北京市政协委员<br>十二届全国青联委员<br>《数学的实践与认识》副主编<br>Enumerative Combinatorics and Applications 编委<br>Advances and Applications in Discrete Mathematics 编委<br>2009- Math Reviews 评论员\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n               </div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n    </aside>\n  </div>\n</article>\n<!--sub_content结束-->\n<!--content结束-->\n<!--footer开始-->\n\n<footer class=\"footer_wrap\">\n  <div class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"lf\">\n      <div class=\"footerList\">\n        <div class=\"footerTitle\"><h3>友情链接</h3></div>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"http://www.pku.edu.cn/\"><i>&gt;</i>北京大学</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.cms.org.cn/\"><i>&gt;</i>中国数学会</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"http://bicmr.pku.edu.cn/\"><i>&gt;</i>北京国际数学研究中心</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"http://www.srmc.pku.edu.cn/index.htm\"><i>&gt;</i>中俄数学中心</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"https://bda.pku.edu.cn/\"><i>&gt;</i>大数据分析与应用技术国家工程实验室</a></li>\n                  <li><a href=\"https://www.stat-center.pku.edu.cn/\"><i>&gt;</i>北京大学统计科学中心</a></li>\n                </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"md\">\n      <div class=\"footerList\">\n        <div class=\"footerTitle\"><!--h3>联系我们</h3--></div>\n        <div class=\"footerContact\">\n          <p>地 址: 北京市海淀区北京大学智华楼</p>\n          <p>邮 编: 100871</p>\n          <p>联系电话：010-62751804</p>\n          <p>邮 箱：mathweb@math.pku.edu.cn</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rt\">\n      <div class=\"footerList footerList1\">\n        <div class=\"code2D\">\n          <img src=\"../../../images/code.jpg\">\n          <p>【 微信公众号 】</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n